snippet.title: Pokémon Sword & Shield DLC Isle of Armor Release Date Trailer Nintendo Switch 2020 HD
snippet.description: This is the official Release Date Trailer for the DLC Expansion pack Pokémon Sword and Shield including Isle of Armor & Crown Tundra with new Forms, Legendary Pokemon and new Gigantamax Forms for Nintendo Switch from Nintendo Pokémon Direct in HD
